title: Seal - Seal II  (Flac) [FrankFoo]
description:
Seal - Seal II (flac)

A far deeper, more enduring outing than his spectacular 1991 debut. 
Producer Trevor Horn calls on a cast of dozens (including Joni Mitchell who duets on the lovely "If I Could" and 
the ubiquitous Jeff Beck) and channels his famous, over-the-top tendencies into a sumptious bed of sound that makes 
Tears for Fears sound minimal. 
Soulful first single "Prayer for the Dying" will set the pace, while "Kiss From A Rose" is a huge ballad.
